title: Haunted
description: Nearly 10 years after Utah mother Susan Powell vanished, private journals, home videos and emails shed new light on what happened to her. Keith Morrison reports. Originally aired on NBC on October 4, 2019.
author: nbcnews.podcasts@gmail.com (NBC News)
